window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Inspired by a haunting true story....</i></b>&nbsp;</p> <p>When Rowan and her family move into the 1800s home nestled in the woods on a bluff near Lake Michigan, she's looking forward to a summer reprieve. However, she soon discovers that Helme House harbors dark secrets, including people who have vanished from the house and never been found.&nbsp;</p> <p>As Rowan digs into the history of Helme House, a series of troubling experiences soon become deadly.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Helme House</i> is the second stand-alone novel in the Troubled Spirits Series, where paranormal fiction meets true crime.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Do you believe in ghosts?</i></p>"; 
